NAME
       gnutls_sign_is_secure2 - API function

SYNOPSIS
       #include <gnutls/gnutls.h>

       unsigned gnutls_sign_is_secure2(gnutls_sign_algorithm_t algorithm, unsigned int flags);

ARGUMENTS
       gnutls_sign_algorithm_t algorithm
                   is a sign algorithm

       unsigned int flags
                   zero or GNUTLS_SIGN_FLAG_SECURE_FOR_CERTS

RETURNS
       Non-zero if the provided signature algorithm is considered to be secure.

REPORTING BUGS
       Report bugs to <bugs@gnutls.org>.
       Home page: https://www.gnutls.org

